{"tid":883314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西藏流亡政府　受美國國會援助　每年200萬美元　今年300萬美元","createTime":"2018-10-30T17:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T09:13:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16090b75cea62b913371c05c223075c01444045c","tid":883314,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180325-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E7%B5%A6%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%96%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA1700%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20180325-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA1700%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25B2%25BB&d=oqBhB250KyJ3JSK4hIsUA%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d84a23b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180325-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E7%B5%A6%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%96%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA1700%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/9437CB6B-6F1D-47A7-A833-CEAA280C09E8_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F9437CB6B-6F1D-47A7-A833-CEAA280C09E8_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=c6ce842d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會參議院撥款委員會，近日通過了2018年藏人援助經費。<br />\n<br />\n300萬美元用於強化藏人機構與流亡政府。<br />\n<br />\n此前美聯社曾披露&ldquo;近年美國國會會已批准每年給西藏流亡政府200萬美元的資金&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n美國對藏人的撥款援助由來已久。在2002年，時任美國總統小布什簽署了有關資助流亡藏人的法案，一直延續至今。該法案稱&ldquo;支持西藏人民保護其身份獨立性&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"c20516f7dedf7c805f22e86a5feef1dabf7e2de9","tid":883314,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T22:12:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"078b1f0d86f9180b73ea37266200a354b8415a20","tid":883314,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T23:44:54.000Z","msg":"專登加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88daf9dd56d22a9ccc7a4acc6ddc4b8ceea98553","tid":883314,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d24575fd57e773e9b0a0dcab1529965350055b","tid":883314,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"香港流亡政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cabca14a7f5e4a33ca6f703fdfb57912cdb5ed","tid":883314,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"口交部呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b31afb2a2d28199e9118814c9ddc2345d625df","tid":883314,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"每年用來買靚車，pp，電器電腦"},{"pid":"3d934ff4002b6a3bd8eae38eee36141578f36efa","tid":883314,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"通脹姐"},{"pid":"b80dbc018d020e5f057aee2a9dce71aeedde594c","tid":883314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1ddfba0cf999c91cf8bf3b2fdcfe75f9111f94","tid":883314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}